The '''Xal 3 Armorers' Confederacy''', originally known simply as the '''Armorers' Confederacy''', was a band of outlaw armorers and weapons technicians that was originally based on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Xal 3]]. They were forced off of their homeworld and forced to seek refuge in the [[Krasho Salt Rifts]] on the planet of [[Sarafur]] during the last years of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. The Confederacy was known for its skills in repairing almost every form of combat [[Armor/Legends|armor]], and their custom armor designs were considered some of the best in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]].<ref name="Tessent">{{GamerCite|9|Race for the Tessent}}</ref>

